item.title: CVE-2023-0274|2024-08-02T05:02:44.147Z -- unknown -- url%20params
item.description: The URL Params WordPress plugin before 2.5 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
